2. The 1st day of June 2025 is appointed as the day on which Part 2 of the 
Health Insurance (Amendment) and Health (Provision of Menopause Products) 
Act 2024 (No. 42 of 2024) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

29 May, 2025. 

JENNIFER CARROLL MACNEILL, 

Minister for Health. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 3rd June, 2025.
